ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX sd223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX ex: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223/data/lbnl-example-2#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?zone ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  # Zone instances\\n  ?zone a sd223:Zone .\\n  \\n  # ----- Property acquisition (direct OR indirect) -----\\n  {\\n    # Directly attached property\\n    ?zone sd223:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  } UNION {\\n    # Indirect: two \\""connected\\"" hops to a RoomDomainSpace that contains the property\\n    ?zone (sd223:connected){2} ?ds .\\n    ?ds a ex:RoomDomainSpace .\\n    ?ds sd223:contains ?prop .\\n  }\\n  \\n  # Property label\\n  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .\\n  \\n  # External reference associated with the property\\n  ?prop sd223:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  \\n  # Only consider external references where writable is false\\n  ?extRef brick:writable false .\\n  \\n  # Retrieve the alc endpoint and the MPC endpoint\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint .\\n  ?extRef brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint .\\n}\\nORDER BY ?zone ?propLabel""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 15, 38, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[ToolCallPart(tool_name='final_result', args='{""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX sd223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX ex: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223/data/lbnl-example-2#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?zone ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  # Zones\\n  ?zone a sd223:Zone .\\n  \\n  # Direct property or via two-step connection to RoomDomainSpace containing property\\n  {\\n    ?zone sd223:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  } UNION {\\n    ?zone sd223:connected ?mid .\\n    ?mid sd223:connected ?ds .\\n    ?ds a ex:RoomDomainSpace .\\n    ?ds sd223:contains ?prop .\\n  }\\n  \\n  # Property label\\n  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .\\n  \\n  # External reference with writable false\\n  ?prop sd223:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  ?extRef brick:writable false .\\n  \\n  # Retrieve endpoints\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint .\\n  ?extRef brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint .\\n}\\nORDER BY ?zone ?propLabel""}', tool_call_id='chatcmpl-tool-8d0a8604e2f8488f8c39d8135ddfd335', part_kind='tool-call')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 15, 42, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?zone ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  # Zone entity\\n  ?zone a s223:Zone .\\n  \\n  # Either the zone directly has a property\\n  { ?zone s223:hasProperty ?prop . }\\n  UNION\\n  # Or the zone reaches a RoomDomainSpace in two \\""connected\\"" steps, then that space contains the property\\n  {\\n    ?zone s223:connected ?intermediate .\\n    ?intermediate s223:connected ?roomSpace .\\n    ?roomSpace a s223:RoomDomainSpace .\\n    ?roomSpace s223:contains ?prop .\\n  }\\n  \\n  # Property label\\n  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .\\n  \\n  # External reference of the property\\n  ?prop s223:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  \\n  # Only include external references that are not writable\\n  ?extRef brick:writable false .\\n  \\n  # Retrieve the Alc endpoint and MPC endpoint from the external reference\\n  OPTIONAL { ?extRef brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint . }\\n  OPTIONAL { ?extRef brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint . }\\n}\\nORDER BY ?zone ?propLabel""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 15, 47, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX ashrae: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX ex: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223/data/lbnl-example-2#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?zone ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  ?zone a ashrae:Zone .\\n  {\\n    # Property directly attached to the Zone\\n    ?zone ashrae:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  } UNION {\\n    # Property reached via two \\""connected\\"" hops to a RoomDomainSpace then \\""contains\\""\\n    ?zone (ashrae:connected){2} ?roomSpace .\\n    ?roomSpace a ex:RoomDomainSpace .\\n    ?roomSpace ashrae:contains ?prop .\\n  }\\n  # Property label\\n  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .\\n  # Only include properties that are not writable\\n  ?prop brick:writable false .\\n  # External reference information\\n  ?prop ashrae:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint .\\n  ?extRef brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint .\\n}\\nLIMIT 100""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 16, 57, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX sd223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX ex: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223/data/lbnl-example-2#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?zone ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  # Zone instances\\n  ?zone a sd223:Zone .\\n  \\n  # ----- Property acquisition (direct OR indirect) -----\\n  {\\n    # Directly attached property\\n    ?zone sd223:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  } UNION {\\n    # Indirect: two \\""connected\\"" hops to a RoomDomainSpace that contains the property\\n    ?zone (sd223:connected){2} ?ds .\\n    ?ds a ex:RoomDomainSpace .\\n    ?ds sd223:contains ?prop .\\n  }\\n  \\n  # Property label\\n  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .\\n  \\n  # External reference associated with the property\\n  ?prop sd223:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  \\n  # Only consider external references where writable is false\\n  ?extRef brick:writable false .\\n  \\n  # Retrieve the alc endpoint and the MPC endpoint\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint .\\n  ?extRef brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint .\\n}\\nORDER BY ?zone ?propLabel""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 15, 38, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?zone ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  # Zone entity\\n  ?zone a s223:Zone .\\n  \\n  # Either the zone directly has a property\\n  { ?zone s223:hasProperty ?prop . }\\n  UNION\\n  # Or the zone reaches a RoomDomainSpace in two \\""connected\\"" steps, then that space contains the property\\n  {\\n    ?zone s223:connected ?intermediate .\\n    ?intermediate s223:connected ?roomSpace .\\n    ?roomSpace a s223:RoomDomainSpace .\\n    ?roomSpace s223:contains ?prop .\\n  }\\n  \\n  # Property label\\n  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .\\n  \\n  # External reference of the property\\n  ?prop s223:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  \\n  # Only include external references that are not writable\\n  ?extRef brick:writable false .\\n  \\n  # Retrieve the Alc endpoint and MPC endpoint from the external reference\\n  OPTIONAL { ?extRef brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint . }\\n  OPTIONAL { ?extRef brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint . }\\n}\\nORDER BY ?zone ?propLabel""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 15, 47, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX ashrae: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX ex: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223/data/lbnl-example-2#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?zone ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  ?zone a ashrae:Zone .\\n  {\\n    # Property directly attached to the Zone\\n    ?zone ashrae:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  } UNION {\\n    # Property reached via two \\""connected\\"" hops to a RoomDomainSpace then \\""contains\\""\\n    ?zone (ashrae:connected){2} ?roomSpace .\\n    ?roomSpace a ex:RoomDomainSpace .\\n    ?roomSpace ashrae:contains ?prop .\\n  }\\n  # Property label\\n  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .\\n  # Only include properties that are not writable\\n  ?prop brick:writable false .\\n  # External reference information\\n  ?prop ashrae:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint .\\n  ?extRef brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint .\\n}\\nLIMIT 100""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 16, 57, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?property ?label ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  # Zones (including those reachable via room domain spaces and chained connections)\\n  ?zone a s223:Zone .\\n  ?zone (s223:hasProperty | s223:contains/s223:hasProperty | s223:connectedThrough/s223:hasProperty) ?property .\\n  \\n  # Property must be readonly (writable = false)\\n  brick:writable false .\\n  ?property brick:writable false .\\n  \\n  # Labels\\n  ?property rdfs:label ?label .\\n  \\n  # External reference and its endpoints (alc via brick:endpoint, mpc via brick:mpc_db_name)\\n  ?property s223:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint .\\n  ?extRef brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint .\\n}\\nORDER BY ?label""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 17, 6, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[ToolCallPart(tool_name='final_result', args='{""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?property ?label ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  # Identify all zones\\n  ?zone a s223:Zone .\\n  \\n  # Gather properties directly on the zone, on rooms within the zone, and via chained connections\\n  {\\n    ?zone s223:hasProperty ?property .\\n  } UNION {\\n    ?zone s223:hasDomainSpace ?ds .\\n    ?ds s223:contains ?room .\\n    ?room s223:hasProperty ?property .\\n  } UNION {\\n    ?zone s223:connectedThrough* ?conn .\\n    ?conn s223:hasProperty ?property .\\n  }\\n  \\n  # Property must be read\\u2011only (writable = false)\\n  ?property brick:writable \\""false\\""^^xsd:boolean .\\n  \\n  # Get human\\u2011readable label\\n  ?property rdfs:label ?label .\\n  \\n  # External reference and its endpoints (alc via brick:endpoint, mpc via brick:mpc_db_name)\\n  ?property s223:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint .\\n  ?extRef brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint .\\n}\\nORDER BY ?label""}', tool_call_id='chatcmpl-tool-ed0f9f30957e45ccb8fd9c464d67f781', part_kind='tool-call')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 17, 11, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX ash: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?property ?label ?endpoint\\nWHERE {\\n  # Zones (including HVAC zones)\\n  ?zone a ash:Zone .\\n\\n  # Follow any chain of domainspace, containment or property links to reach a property\\n  ?zone (ash:hasDomainSpace|ash:contains|ash:hasProperty)+ ?property .\\n\\n  # The node reached must be a property (observable or actuatable)\\n  ?property a ?propClass .\\n  FILTER(?propClass IN (ash:QuantifiableObservableProperty,\\n                        ash:EnumeratedObservableProperty,\\n                        ash:QuantifiableActuatableProperty,\\n                        ash:EnumeratedActuatableProperty))\\n\\n  # Readonly: no writable flag set to true\\n  FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?property brick:writable true }\\n\\n  # Humanreadable label\\n  ?property rdfs:label ?label .\\n\\n  # External reference and its endpoints (alc and mpc)\\n  ?property ash:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?endpoint .\\n  FILTER(?endpoint IN (\\""alc\\"", \\""mpc\\""))\\n}\\nORDER BY ?property ?endpoint""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 17, 17, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[ToolCallPart(tool_name='final_result', args='{""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX ash: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?property ?label ?endpoint\\nWHERE {\\n  # Any zone (including HVAC zones)\\n  ?zone a ash:Zone .\\n\\n  # Traverse domain space, containment, or property relations (any length) to reach a property\\n  ?zone (ash:hasDomainSpace|ash:contains|ash:hasProperty)+ ?property .\\n\\n  # The reached node must be a property of one of the recognized classes\\n  VALUES ?propClass { ash:QuantifiableObservableProperty ash:EnumeratedObservableProperty\\n                     ash:QuantifiableActuatableProperty ash:EnumeratedActuatableProperty }\\n  ?property a ?propClass .\\n\\n  # Exclude any property that is marked as writable\\n  FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?property brick:writable true }\\n\\n  # Get the human\\u2011readable label\\n  ?property rdfs:label ?label .\\n\\n  # External reference and its endpoints (alc and mpc)\\n  ?property ash:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?endpoint .\\n  FILTER(?endpoint IN (\\""alc\\"", \\""mpc\\""))\\n}\\nORDER BY ?property ?endpoint""}', tool_call_id='chatcmpl-tool-1960ff3ae0fa42f2a31daea23c664b60', part_kind='tool-call')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 17, 22, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX bldg: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX ext: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?property ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  # Zones (including HVAC zones)\\n  ?zone a bldg:Zone .\\n  # Direct properties of the zone\\n  ?zone bldg:hasProperty ?property .\\n  \\n  # Also include properties of rooms that are contained in the zone (RoomDomainSpace -> PhysicalSpace)\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone bldg:contains|bldg:encloses ?room .\\n    ?room a bldg:PhysicalSpace .\\n    ?room bldg:hasProperty ?property .\\n  }\\n  \\n  # Also follow chained connections (one hop) to pick up properties attached to connection points belonging to the zone\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone bldg:hasConnectionPoint ?cp .\\n    ?cp bldg:hasProperty ?property .\\n  }\\n  \\n  # Property label\\n  ?property rdfs:label ?propLabel .\\n  \\n  # Property must be readonly (Brick:writable false or absent)\\n  FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?property brick:writable true }\\n  \\n  # External reference with endpoints\\n  ?property bldg:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint .\\n  FILTER(CONTAINS(LCASE(STR(?alcEndpoint)), \\""alc\\""))\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?mpcEndpoint .\\n  FILTER(CONTAINS(LCASE(STR(?mpcEndpoint)), \\""mpc\\""))\\n}\\nORDER BY ?property""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 17, 26, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[ToolCallPart(tool_name='final_result', args='{""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX bldg: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?property ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  # Zones (including HVAC zones)\\n  ?zone a bldg:Zone .\\n  \\n  # Direct properties of the zone\\n  OPTIONAL { ?zone bldg:hasProperty ?property . }\\n  \\n  # Properties of rooms (PhysicalSpace) contained in the zone\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone bldg:contains|bldg:encloses ?room .\\n    ?room a bldg:PhysicalSpace .\\n    ?room bldg:hasProperty ?property .\\n  }\\n  \\n  # Properties attached to connection points belonging to the zone (one hop)\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone bldg:hasConnectionPoint ?cp .\\n    ?cp bldg:hasProperty ?property .\\n  }\\n  \\n  # Ensure we have a property\\n  FILTER (BOUND(?property))\\n  \\n  # Property label\\n  ?property rdfs:label ?propLabel .\\n  \\n  # Read\\u2011only: no Brick:writable true triple\\n  FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?property brick:writable true }\\n  \\n  # External reference with endpoints containing \\""alc\\"" and \\""mpc\\""\\n  ?property bldg:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint .\\n  FILTER (CONTAINS(LCASE(STR(?alcEndpoint)), \\""alc\\""))\\n  ?extRef brick:endpoint ?mpcEndpoint .\\n  FILTER (CONTAINS(LCASE(STR(?mpcEndpoint)), \\""mpc\\""))\\n}\\nORDER BY ?property""}', tool_call_id='chatcmpl-tool-abcce16463434968a054f50634cf7e38', part_kind='tool-call')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 1, 17, 30, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')
